data.title: General Officer Announcement dtd 24 October 2001
data.text:
The Chief of Staff, Army announces the assignment of the following

general officers:

Brigadier General (Promotable) Charles H. Swannack, Jr. from Commanding General, Joint Readiness Training Center and Fort Polk, Fort Polk, Louisiana to Commander, Multi-National Division (North), Stabilization Force-11, Bosnia-Herzegovina with a report date to be determined.

Brigadier General Jason K. Kamiya from Assistant Division Commander (Support), 101st Airborne Division (Air Assault), Fort Campbell, Kentucky to Commanding General, Joint Readiness Training Center and Fort Polk, Fort Polk, Louisiana with a report date to be determined.
